/a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AudioContext\"><code>AudioContext</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/AudioDestinationNode\"><code>AudioDestinationNode</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AudioListener\"><code>AudioListener</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/AudioNode\"><code>AudioNode</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AudioParam\"><code>AudioParam</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AudioProcessingEvent\"><code>AudioProcessingEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AudioScheduledSourceNode\"><code>AudioScheduledSourceNode</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AudioWorklet\"><code>AudioWorklet</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AudioWorkletGlobalScope\"><code>AudioWorkletGlobalScope</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AudioWorkletNode\"><code>AudioWorkletNode</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AudioWorkletProcessor\"><code>AudioWorkletProcessor</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/BaseAudioContext\"><code>BaseAudioContext</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/BiquadFilterNode\"><code>BiquadFilterNode</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ChannelMergerNode\"><code>ChannelMergerNode</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ChannelSplitterNode\"><code>ChannelSplitterNode</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ConstantSourceNode\"><code>ConstantSourceNode</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ConvolverNode\"><code>ConvolverNode</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DelayNode\"><code>DelayNode</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DynamicsCompressorNode\"><code>DynamicsCompressorNode</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/IIRFilterNode\"><code>IIRFilterNode</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaElementAudioSourceNode\"><code>MediaElementAudioSourceNode</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaStreamAudioDestinationNode\"><code>MediaStreamAudioDestinationNode</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaStreamAudioSourceNode\"><code>MediaStreamAudioSourceNode</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/OfflineAudioCompletionEvent\"><code>OfflineAudioCompletionEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/OfflineAudioContext\"><code>OfflineAudioContext</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/OscillatorNode\"><code>OscillatorNode</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PannerNode\"><code>PannerNode</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PeriodicWave\"><code>PeriodicWave</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/StereoPannerNode\"><code>StereoPannerNode</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WaveShaperNode\"><code>WaveShaperNode</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"sect1\">\n<p>Die&nbsp;<code>GainNode</code> Schnittstelle ermöglicht eine Verstärkung (engl. gain) eines&nbsp;Signals, was&nbsp;als veränderte&nbsp;Lautstärke wahrgenommen wird. Es handelt sich um&nbsp;ein <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/AudioNode\"><code>AudioNode</code></a> audio-verarbeitendes Modul, das&nbsp;ein Eingabesignal mit einer gewissen Verstärkung (die auch negativ sein kann) versieht,&nbsp;und es an den Ausgang weiterleitet. Ein&nbsp;<code>GainNode</code>&nbsp;hat immer genau einen Eingang und einen Ausgang, beide mit derselben Anzahl an Kanälen.</p>\n</div>\n\n<p>Verstärkung&nbsp;ist ein Wert ohne Einheit, der sich über die Zeit ändert. Er wird mit allen zeitlich korrespondierenden Samples aller Eingangskanäle multipliziert, um das Signal zu verändern.&nbsp; Ändert sich der Wert, wird der neue Wert durch einen&nbsp;\"de-zippering\" Algorithmus angewendet, um unästhetisches Klick-Artifakte&nbsp;im Signal&nbsp;zu vermeiden.</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"The GainNode is increasing the gain of the output.\" src=\"https://mdn.mozillademos.org/files/5085/WebAudioGainNode.png\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n\n<table class=\"properties\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Anzahl der Eingänge</th>\n   <td><code>1</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Anzahl der Ausgänge</th>\n   <td><code>1</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Kanalzählmethode</th>\n   <td><code>\"max\"</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Anzahl Kanäle</th>\n   <td><code>2</code> (not used in the default count mode)</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Kanalinterpretation</th>\n   <td><code>\"speakers\"</code></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"eigenschaften","title":"Eigenschaften","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>Inherits properties from its parent, </em><em><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/AudioNode\"><code>AudioNode</code></a></em>.</p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"gainnode.gain_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GainNode/gain\"><code>GainNode.gain</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"Dieser Wert kann nicht verändert werden.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Schreibgeschützt </span></dt>\n <dd>Ist ein&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AudioParam#a-rate\">a-rate</a> <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AudioParam\"><code>AudioParam</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> der das Ausmaß der Verstärkung angibt.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"methoden","title":"Methoden","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>Keine spezifischen Methoden; erbt die Methoden der Elternklasse , </em><em><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/AudioNode\"><code>AudioNode</code></a></em>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beispiel","title":"Beispiel","isH3":false,"content":"<p>{{page(\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AudioContext.createGain\",\"Example\")}}</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikationen","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/webaudio/#the-gainnode-interface\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Web Audio API<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'GainNode' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Empfehlung</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_kompatibilität","title":"Browser Kompatibilität","isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect2\"><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect3\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Wir konvertieren die Kompatibilitätsdaten in ein maschinenlesbares JSON Format</a></strong>.\n            Diese Kompatibilitätstabelle liegt noch im alten Format vor,\n            denn die darin enthaltenen Daten wurden noch nicht konvertiert.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Finde heraus wie du helfen kannst! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect4\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Mobile</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div></div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari (WebKit)</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td>10.0<span class=\"inlineIndicator prefixBox prefixBoxInline\" title=\"prefix\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Vendor_Prefix\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">webkit (en-US)</a></span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/25\" title=\"Veröffentlicht am 2013-10-29.\">25.0</a> (25.0)&nbsp;</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span></td>\n   <td>15.0<span class=\"inlineIndicator prefixBox prefixBoxInline\" title=\"prefix\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Vendor_Prefix\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">webkit (en-US)</a></span><br>\n    22</td>\n   <td>6.0<span class=\"inlineIndicator prefixBox prefixBoxInline\" title=\"prefix\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Vendor_Prefix\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">webkit (en-US)</a></span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Firefox OS</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n   <th>Chrome for Android</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td>26.0</td>\n   <td>1.2</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td>33.0</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"siehe_auch","title":"Siehe auch","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Audio_API/Using_Web_Audio_API\">Die Web Audio API</a>&nbsp;benutzen</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Eigenschaften","id":"eigenschaften"},{"text":"Methoden","id":"methoden"},{"text":"Beispiel","id":"beispiel"},{"text":"Spezifikationen","id":"spezifikationen"},{"text":"Browser Kompatibilität","id":"browser_kompatibilität"},{"text":"Siehe auch","id":"siehe_auch"}],"summary":"Die GainNode Schnittstelle ermöglicht eine Verstärkung (engl. gain) eines Signals, was als veränderte Lautstärke wahrgenommen wird. Es handelt sich um ein AudioNode audio-verarbeitendes Modul, das ein Eingabesignal mit einer gewissen Verstärkung (die auch negativ sein kann) versieht, und es an den Ausgang weiterleitet. Ein GainNode hat immer genau einen Eingang und einen Ausgang, beide mit derselben Anzahl an Kanälen.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"GainNode","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"GainNode","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"GainNode","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"GainNode","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/api/gainnode","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/api/gainnode/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für En